  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is a one-day international cross-sectional nutritional audit in one ward. The
      purpose of this study is to generate a risk and level of nutritional intervention profile for
      an individual unit/ward based on case-mix, structures and social environment.
    </textblock>
